  <abstract format="text/html" language="en" script="Latn">
    <p>This specification defines a model for the relationships between resources on the Web ("links") and the type of those relationships ("link relation types").</p>
    <p>It also defines the serialisation of such links in HTTP headers with the Link header field.</p>
